pardus-flatpak-gui (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Improve "Install" and "Uninstall" menu item functions
  * Popup menu when right click instead of left click
  * Update Info window appearance and functionality
  * View remote name as "FlatHub" if it is "flathub"
  * Add "Cancel" button for installing, uninstalling and updating
  * Add confirmation dialogs before installing and uninstalling
  * Update message dialog titles and make them translatable
  * Update documentation

